                    <div class="text-size-medium text-weight-bold w-embed">
                      Carta de Paulo Luan
                    </div><div>Dev Front-End e Co-Fundador #jobnagringa</div>
                  </div>
                </div><a
                  href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pauloluan/recent-activity/"
